 ø  Description

    ISPF Services search the variable pools for access to variables.



    The Search Order is:



       1.  Function Pool

       2.  Shared Pool

       3.  Profile Pool



 ø  Functionality

    When a variable is found, it is always maintained in the Function Po

    A variable found in the SHARED or PROFILE pool is copied/created in
    Function Pool.
